data.revised_prompt: Create a detailed image of the Seattle skyline, drawing inspiration from the Post-Impressionist style of Van Gogh, using his key characteristics such as his unique brushwork, vibrant color palette and swirling skies. The skyline should feature notable landmarks like the Space Needle and Mt. Rainier in the background. The image should evoke a sense of emotion akin to what is felt in Van Gogh's works, perfectly marrying his charms with the scenic beauty of Seattle.
